{"tid":2094813,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"俄外交部：擴大版G7峰會需要中國參與","createTime":"2020-07-05T03:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T06:04:31.000Z","uid":278587,"like":1,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9e97d30d5c36a86298f2e5b578946bcd15a6f687","tid":2094813,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200705/356397864110395392.jpeg/7Ns1OtrmFzOeEGqQElmDiQBoGqjoR0K0j5SOjo-Ujo4?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200705%2F356397864110395392.jpeg%2F7Ns1OtrmFzOeEGqQElmDiQBoGqjoR0K0j5SOjo-Ujo4%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=96b6d4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯外交部副部長里亞布科夫（Sergei Ryabkov）7月4日表示，俄方堅持中國也應要列為擴大版七國集團（G7）峰會的會議成員。<br />\n<br />\n里亞布科夫告訴俄羅斯媒體塔斯社（Tass）稱：「這個所謂的擴大版G7構想存在缺陷，因為不清楚提出這項倡議的人計劃如何處理中國因素，」「沒有中國，根本不可能討論現今世界的任何議題。」<br />\n<br />\n美國駐俄大使沙利文（John Sullivan）3日告訴俄羅斯電視台RBC TV，華府已「與俄羅斯外交部及其他G7政府討論關於俄羅斯是否能在G7扮演適當角色」。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）5月30日宣布把G7峰會的舉行日期推遲到至少9月之後，並將邀請澳洲、俄羅斯、韓國及印度出席會議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/494090/俄外交部-擴大版g7峰會需要中國參與\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2F494090%2F%E4%BF%84%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8-%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7%E7%89%88g7%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%83%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=b035ba7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/494090/俄外交部-擴大版g7峰會需要中國參與</a>"},{"pid":"e4ecdfa29f470483fe309d4b4813e71715c91a5b","tid":2094813,"uid":274435,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:53:05.000Z","msg":"收檔啦俄狗<br />\n有咩資格俾意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff02296c5d64604902c16b3391b3ff6ec36bc16","tid":2094813,"uid":24270,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:58:38.000Z","msg":"變G6 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f1ff793133aa9742821aa058c9202ea24cdb92","tid":2094813,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:05:44.000Z","msg":"等大家羞辱支那？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0544a4c00ad700e916e465fc9c0907b5971c5c7e","tid":2094813,"uid":143241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:06:14.000Z","msg":"有中國咁俄羅斯就會多一票"},{"pid":"c0072adfb915507b2161024ca3b965c3686befdc","tid":2094813,"uid":9542,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"trump 搞d10 算啦，加埋俄狗入去一定無偈傾"},{"pid":"ab622f9c259ba3ceefa08053a902a228734e5a73","tid":2094813,"uid":64345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dff02296c5d64604902c16b3391b3ff6ec36bc16","tid":2094813,"uid":24270,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:58:38.000Z","msg":"變G6 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:11:27.000Z","msg":"本身G8, 普京出局變咗G7"},{"pid":"a7239e92551be4826f8d3cc358cd7d4211688613","tid":2094813,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0072adfb915507b2161024ca3b965c3686befdc","tid":2094813,"uid":9542,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"trump 搞d10 算啦，加埋俄狗入去一定無偈傾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:11:43.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯唔係入面既話傾完等於無傾"},{"pid":"b71aca7a1facc9738dd3c7638a62fecdcdd30565","tid":2094813,"uid":51840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T05:02:07.000Z","msg":"G7本身係自己友俱樂部"},{"pid":"d4e9d2a967faed1855ca7eee5a6600ee011db159","tid":2094813,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T05:30:05.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯 中國 伊朗 北韓 巴基斯坦 委內瑞拉 塞爾維亞"},{"pid":"4fafbdf32e6de892d6ea08d0a9484ed51c92632c","tid":2094813,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c